                        <Font name="Segoe UI" size="16.0" />
                     </font>
                  </Text>
                  <Text layoutX="30.0" layoutY="282.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="Understanding the behavior of subatomic particles is essential in explaining chemical properties and reactions. Isotopes are atoms of the same element with different numbers of neutrons, affecting atomic mass but not chemical behavior. Ions, on the other hand, form when atoms gain or lose electrons, leading to charged species that play crucial roles in chemical reactions." textAlignment="JUSTIFY" wrappingWidth="727.7760620117188">
