                  <Text layoutX="30.0" layoutY="977.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="Through stoichiometry, students learn to convert between mass, moles, and volume, enabling them to determine how much of a substance is needed or produced in a given reaction. Mastery of this topic is essential for practical applications in laboratory and industrial settings." textAlignment="JUSTIFY" wrappingWidth="727.7760620117188">
